text: Compassvale LRT Station is a light rail transit station in Sengkang, Singapore. It opened on 18 January 2003. It is on the east loop of Sengkang LRT Line. == Name == Its name came from the street it is located on. It is located at Compassvale Street. == Sources == == Other websites == https://www.sbstransit.com.sg Category:Sengkang Category:Light Rail Transit (Singapore) stations
title: Compassvale LRT Station
